feed.title: [ann] Bitcoin Core version 0.9.2 has been released

entry.title: [ann] Bitcoin Core version 0.9.2 has been released
entry.summary: In an email conversation between Jesus Cea and Wladimir on June 17, 2014, Wladimir reported an issue while running bitcoin-qt under Ubuntu 10.04. Specifically, he received a "symbol lookup error" stating that there was an undefined symbol "_ZN10QTextCodec11validCodecsEv". Jesus asked if the issue occurred with the release candidate.
